{"tid":2499502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴基斯坦有酒店遭汽車炸彈襲擊多人死傷　報道指中國大使或是襲擊目標","createTime":"2021-04-22T02:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T05:35:58.000Z","uid":366655,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e8e1681399d81a153b031538caf7e65d5f5f0a9f","tid":2499502,"uid":366655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:37:07.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】巴基斯坦俾路支省首府奎達市一間酒店發生炸彈襲擊，造成至少4死11傷。報道指，中國駐巴基斯坦大使可能是襲擊目標。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地周三晚，涉事酒店停車場一部裝有炸彈的汽車發生爆炸，附近其他汽車受波及和起火，警察封鎖現場調查，救護車到場接載傷者到鄰近的醫院救治。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐巴基斯坦大使農融當時正在奎達訪問，並入住事發酒店，但他事發時不在酒店內，未有受傷。<br />\n<br />\n塔利班武裝組織的巴基斯坦分支事後承認以汽車炸彈發動自殺式襲擊。英國廣播公司報道指，中國大使可能是今次的襲擊目標，巴基斯坦當局正全面調查事件。<br />\n<br />\nlink：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=432006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432006&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=af2e9c12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432006&h=19f8583b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=432006</a>"},{"pid":"69332fafa2a43e41ded3f0143865f53a255ccd07","tid":2499502,"uid":366655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:38:36.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"71767a1cd7cc440a7be6dd36a34a7f0dd11cf913","tid":2499502,"uid":366655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:38:46.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"b6a371d80c90d89c0ddecbd9c58d8493dfc85cda","tid":2499502,"uid":366655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:38:57.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"9af22688b7c58c1414ac9a44cd07f12eb674712d","tid":2499502,"uid":366655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:39:14.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"389623a629fa0333fd6cc9b14fed32b9b42ef811","tid":2499502,"uid":366655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite